method.name: network_group_config
method.description: This procedure creates, modifies and deletes network topologies - IPv4 or Ipv6 Prefix Pools, Simulated routers to design network grid or topologies.

description.text: enables/disables device.

Scenario element IPV4_prefix connector is connecting to for dual-stack-prefix mode.
Scenario element IPV6_prefix connector is connecting to for dual-stack-prefix mode.
Mode of the procedure call. Valid options are: create modify delete
The type of topology route to create.
